{
  "texts": [
    "High-resolution anatomical characteristics were retrieved that aids latent image learning, decompression, and edge training proves beneficial.",
    "To conduct qualitative and quantitative evaluations, three separate variant and in-variant blur were employed in data -sets from Lai, GoPro, and Kohler.",
    "Comparing the suggested method to various preprocessing strategies for image analysis, experiments revealed that it was effective in lowering blur while maintaining structural qualities.",
    "Furthermore, the proposed strategy for huge data analysis was proven to be effective across a few publicly accessible datasets.",
    "Optimal solution for limitationsThe limitations discussed can be resolved by optimization of parameters used in training by generators and discriminators, by selection of activation function, or by using batch normalizations."
  ]
}